Italian Finance Minister Giulio Tremonti May Resign, La Repubblica Reports

-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a   a n d   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 
2011-06-28T05:15:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/italy-finance-minister-giulio-tremonti-may-resign-repubblica-reports.html
Italian Finance Minister  Giulio
Tremonti  may resign following criticism by members of the
government coalition over his budget measures, daily la
Repubblica reported, without saying where it got the
information.  Lorenzo Bini Smaghi, who is due to leave his position as
European Central Bank Executive Board member, may be called on
to replace Tremonti, the Italian newspaper reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jerrold Colten at 
 jcolten@bloomberg.net  